I. Redis Centos7 Install
ref: https://redis.io/download
$ wget http://download.redis.io/releases/redis-4.0.11.tar.gz
$ tar xzf redis-4.0.11.tar.gz
$ cd redis-4.0.11
$ make

#test
$ cd src
$ make test

#start server and enter cli
$ src/redis-server [redis.conf]

#shutdown server
$ src/redis -cli shutdown

#Enter cli
$ src/redis-cli 
#Enter cli and avoid unidentifiable Chinese code 
$ src/redis -cli --raw 


II. Config to allow Remote Connection
# config redis.conf
bind 0.0.0.0
protected-mode no

#turn off os firewall
sudo service iptables stop


III. Java access Redis by Jedis
ref: https://github.com/xetorthio/jedis
     https://redis.io/clients#java

First download Jedis.jar
Then code like:

	public static void main(String[] args)
	{
		// 连接本地的 Redis 服务
		Jedis jedis = new Jedis("192.168.102.52", 6379);
		System.out.println("连接成功");
		// 查看服务是否运行
		System.out.println("ping: " + jedis.ping());
		System.out.println("foo: " + jedis.get("foo"));
		
	}


